  EffectDiscription_ENG: "\uFF1CBlocker\uFF1E \n[When Digivolving] [On Deletion]
    If your opponent has 10 or fewer cards in their trash, trash the top 3 cards
    of both players' decks. Then, if your opponent has 10 or more cards in their
    trash, you may play 1 level 4 or lower [Evil] or [Fallen Angel] Digimon card
    from your trash without paying the cost."
  InheritedEffectDiscription_JPN: 
  InheritedEffectDiscription_ENG: "[When Attacking] [Once Per Turn] This Digimon
